---
title: The Alchemist's Hearth
layout: layouts/base
section: "alchemists-hearth"
---
<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32 flex flex-col gap-16">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="text-center space-y-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-accent">The Alchemist's Hearth</h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-secondary max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      My kitchen experiments, cooking failures, and the occasional dish that actually turns out great.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Introduction -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto text-muted max-w-3xl">
    <p>
      I love cooking. Sometimes things work out, sometimes they don't. This is where I write 
      about what I'm making, recipes I'm trying, and whatever I'm learning as I go.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you're into cooking or just curious, welcome. Let's see what we can burn together.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- List of posts -->
  <div class="space-y-12">
    {% for post in collections.alchemistsHearth %}
      <article class="space-y-2 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-2 text-primary text-accent capitalize">
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
        </h2>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
